title: 08/05/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 08/05/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP is joined by former NFL lineman Ross Tucker, who discusses which 6 teams he thinks are legitimate contenders for the Super Bowl this season. Cowboys Radio Color Analyst Babe Laufenberg explains which side of the ball has to be great for the Cowboys to be successful this year. And Dodgers Radio Play by play announcer describes what the scene was like this week at Dodger Stadium with the Astros in town.
